net.neurowork.mobile.android.fw
Class NextLevel

java.lang.Object
  net.neurowork.mobile.android.fw.NextLevel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class NextLevel
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Represents a NextLevel in the application. A NextLevel is a levelId-dataId pair, for access to a particular screen in the application. The NextLevel is used to relate levelId from app.xml file with dataId from other xml file.

Author:
Jorge E. Villaverde
